A machine learning project designed to detect fraudulent financial transactions using supervised classification techniques. This system analyzes transaction patterns and identifies anomalies that may indicate fraud.

ğŸš€ Project Overview

Financial fraud is increasing with the rise of online transactions. This project builds a predictive model to classify transactions as:

