ğŸ“Š Dataset Description

Typical features in the dataset:

Column	Description
TransactionID	Unique transaction identifier
Amount	Transaction amount
TransactionType	Online / POS / Transfer
OldBalance	Previous account balance
NewBalance	New account balance
CustomerID	Linked customer ID
IsFraud	Target label (1 = Fraud, 0 = Not Fraud)
